txt.en: Barricades inside the city will jeopardize the Rangers' attempts to infiltrate Minas Morgul, and should be destroyed.\n\nReport to Dolenthol when the work is done.

'Your assistance is most welcome! With these barricades destroyed, it will be easier for our forces to slip without notice past unfriendly eyes.'
Gothmog's forces have built a series of fortifications throughout the area.  Dorgam asked you to destroy them.
